    public interface UniversalIndefiniteGraph<N,​E,​NP,​EP>
extends IndefiniteGraph<N,​E>
    A universal graph, i.e., with (possibly empty) node and edge properties. For a documentation on the concept of "universal", see UniversalTransitionSystem.
